OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Government officials have apologised   
OL,6, for failing to consult residents about 
OL,7, plans to convert an ex-RAF base into an
OL,8, asylum centre for up to 1,500 people.  
OL,10,FThe Home Office wants to use the former
OL,11,FLinton-on-Ouse site, near York, to     
OL,12,Fhouse asylum seekers while their       
OL,13,Fapplications are being processed.      
OL,15,FThe parish council and residents were  
OL,16,Fnot consulted before the announcement. 
OL,18,FOn Thursday the Home Office apologised 
OL,19,Ffor failing to discuss the plans and   
OL,20,Fsaid it hopes to mend the relationship.
